BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:What do people ask when they first see a Canang Sari and feel conf
 used?
DTSTART;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T000000
DTEND;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T120000
UID:2603065D6gkCJVhU2x33q3v5Hl2g
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/ElvbfdNsckiXa9Ed54hWMA.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:When people first see a canang sari\, they often feel a mixtur
 e of curiosity and confusion. Many wonder\, “What is this small\, intric
 ate offering made of flowers and leaves?” or “Why is it placed in a sp
 ecific corner or on the ground?” Others might ask\, “Does it have a sp
 iritual purpose\, and who is it meant for?” The colours\, scents\, and c
 areful arrangement can feel mysterious\, leaving observers questioning the
 ir meaning and significance. Some even think it’s purely decorative\, un
 aware of the deep intention behind each element. Similarly\, just as the c
 anang sari is a daily practice to invite gratitude and harmony\, Joy Poten
 tial teaches that joy is cultivated intentionally and with awareness. Peop
 le often ask\, “How can I feel joy consistently in my life?” or “Is 
 joy something I am born with\, or can I learn it?” Just as each canang s
 ari is created with care to honour the divine and the present moment\, Joy
  Potential shows that small\, consistent practices can awaken our inner li
 ght. Observers might also ask\, “Do I need to understand the rituals to 
 experience the benefit?” In the same way\, Joy Potential invites individ
 uals to explore joy without needing to grasp all the science or methods at
  once. Both the canang sari and Joy Potential emphasise presence\, intenti
 on\, and transformation. People often feel an initial hesitation\, unsure 
 if they belong in this space of mindfulness and heart-centred practice. Jo
 y Potential encourages stepping in\, exploring\, and allowing the process 
 to work\, just as one would approach a canang sari with curiosity and resp
 ect. Each small action\, whether placing a flower in a basket or practisin
 g a joyful habit\, contributes to a larger sense of peace and fulfilment. 
 Finally\, just like the mystery behind the canang sari draws people to lea
 rn more\, Joy Potential inspires individuals to reconnect with their authe
 ntic joy\, understand its practices\, and integrate them into daily life.
LOCATION:Woolery Mill
URL:https://joypotential.com/canang-sari/
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Bloomington
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Rosencrantz and Guildenstern Are Dead by Tom Stoppard
DTSTART;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T193000
DTEND;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T215000
UID:260213WrYSCxhYwUCTMH2wC-Q1aQ
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/6i1smXuOe0efQDr0u7wFMQ.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Acclaimed as a modern dramatic masterpiece\, Rosencrantz and G
 uildenstern Are Dead is the fabulously inventive tale of Hamlet as told fr
 om the worm's-eye view of the bewildered Rosencrantz and Guildenstern\, tw
 o minor characters in Shakespeare's play. In Tom Stoppard's best-known wor
 k\, this Shakespearean Laurel and Hardy finally get a chance to take the l
 ead role\, but do so in a world where echoes of Waiting for Godot resound\
 , where reality and illusion intermix\, and where fate leads our two heroe
 s to a tragic but inevitable end.
LOCATION:Constellation Playhouse
URL:http://www.eclipseproductionscompany.com
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Bloomington
END:VEVENT
