BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Indiana Brewers Guild Springfest
DTSTART;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260411T140000
DTEND;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260411T180000
UID:26031772EjEEDeskiMnkNeUU0q4w
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/zG7c129HlUqI7pn4Pnesmw.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Join the Indiana Brewers Guild for our annual spring fundraise
 r\, taking place April 11\, 2026  from 2-6p at the The Historic Woolery Mi
 ll in Bloomington.  Sample beers\, ciders\, and more crafted by dozens of 
 breweries and guests while enjoying local food\, shopping\, and games.\n\n
 Early Entry &ndash\; Enter at 2p &amp\; receive a taster glass to enjoy fi
 rst dibs on beers from 30\\+ participating Hoosier breweries and guests\, 
 with a smaller crowd size and shorter lines.  Early Entry guests will also
  receive a limited edition Bloomington Craft Beer Fest pint glass upon exi
 t.\n\nGeneral Admission &ndash\; Enter at 3p and receive a taster glass go
 od for unlimited 3 oz. pours of local beer\, cider and craft cocktails.\n\
 nDesignated Drivers &ndash\; Enter anytime &amp\; enjoy unlimited water\, 
 soda\, and samples of NA beverages from DD vendors.\n\nNo refunds or excha
 nges. This is an all-weather \\(rain\, snow\, sleet\, or shine\\) event.\n
 \nTicket proceeds support the not-for-profit Indiana Brewers Guildand our 
 mission to support\, educate\, promote and legislate on behalf of Hoosier 
 Breweries.\n\nThe Indiana Brewers Guild and our members believe in buildin
 g community one pint\, or tasting glass\, at a time. Grab your friends\, b
 uy your tickets and taste Indiana Craft with us!\n\nAll-weather event. No 
 refunds or exchanges.
LOCATION:Woolery Mill
URL:https://tickets.drinkin.beer/e/springfest?aff=cityspark
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Bloomington
END:VEVENT
