BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:ABRA Cadabra
DTSTART;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260419T193000
DTEND;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260419T214500
UID:260211abWWAr_ZSUu2syiTPG8mjA
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/V4rtUAU-aEW7fZhzOYdUuA.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Attention all ABBA fans! Get ready for a night of glittering 
 costumes\, irresistible melodies\, and pure joy when ABRA Cadabra – the 
 internationally acclaimed ABBA tribute band – takes the stage at Burkirk
 -Chumley Theater in Bloomington on April 19\, 2026 @ 7:30pm.\n\nFor 25 yea
 rs\, ABRA Cadabra has been captivating audiences across the globe with fai
 thful yet fresh performances of ABBA’s timeless hits. From “Dancing Qu
 een” to “Mamma Mia” and “Take a Chance on Me\,” the band blends 
 meticulous musical detail with colorful visuals and an atmosphere designed
  to get audiences on their feet.\n\nThe result is a high-energy\, family-f
 riendly spectacle featuring a live band\, dancers\, dazzling costumes\, an
 d multiple wardrobe changes. Audiences are encouraged to sing\, clap\, and
  dance along\, creating a shared moment of nostalgia and celebration.\n\nC
 onnect with ABRA Cadabra on Facebook & Instagram @ATributeToABBA and onlin
 e at www.iloveabba.com\n\nHere’s what our fans are saying.\n\n“Best s
 how we’ve ever seen!” – Gilberte Nowlan – Moncton\, NB\n\n“I’v
 e seen tributes to ABBA before\, they were great\, but you are the best. I
 f you come back East we will be there!” –Jack Hayward – Fredericton\
 , NB\n\n“Just saw your show in Regina. WOW! You guys are amazing – I t
 ook my \\(80\\+\\) mom and she loved it! The entire group is stunning\, ne
 ver seen any performers acknowledge their entire crew\, go into the audien
