 ement Award \\(Be More Dedicated\\)\, Volunteer of the Year \\(Be More Imp
 actful\\)\, and a Youth Volunteer Award \\(Be More Energized\\). Each reci
 pient will be honored with an award and a $1\,000.00 grant award to the pr
 imary organization they volunteer for.\n\nThe Bloomington Volunteer Networ
 k will also celebrate the City’s progress towards the goal of logging 10
 0\,000 volunteer hours in 2026.\n\nLearn more at www.bloomingtonvolunteer
